title: Russell Wilson and Pregnant Ciara Step Out for Date Night -- See Her Chic Maternity Look!
text: Russell Wilson and Pregnant Ciara Step Out for Date Night -- See Her Chic Maternity Look! by Jennifer Drysdale 8:30 PM PST, February 25, 2017 Photo: Getty Images Ciara is slaying her pregnancy style! The 31-year-old singer took to Instagram on Friday to show off her chic date night look with hubby Russell Wilson, and girl definitely knows how to work her curves! A post shared by Ciara (@ciara) on Feb 24, 2017 at 7:38pm PST The pregnant star was clearly feeling herself, sharing another photo of the ensemble on Saturday. "#Margiela & #TomFord," she wrote alongside the shot. A post shared by Ciara (@ciara) on Feb 25, 2017 at 10:34am PST While Ciara definitely rocked the glam look, she's also not afraid to let her natural beauty shine. In fact, the mother of 2-year-old Future Jr. recently went makeup-free on the red carpet. See more in the video below. RELATED SLIDESHOW
